{"nodes":[{"nodeID":"1454","text":"His suggestion is disturbing unworkable and potentially dangerous","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1455","text":"As someone who has watched several close friends struggle with heroin addiction I have to ask: what is Watters thinking?","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1456","text":"the decision to quit drugs cannot be enforced from the outside.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1457","text":"Locking up addicts against their will would not only violate their rights; it would be likely to prove counter-productive","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1458","text":"Drug workers talk about a  circuit-breaker  the event that triggers a person's decision to quit - a long-suffering partner walking out a valued job being lost. The addict realises what they stand to lose if they don't stop using.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1459","text":"This realisation is an internal one","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1460","text":"Internal decision is opposite to an external one","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1461","text":"Addiction means the person has lost control over their drug use.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1462","text":"Increasing addicts` control over his own life is beneficial","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1463","text":"The addiction cannot be  cured  by reducing still further that person's control over their own lives and circumstances as Watters is suggesting.","type":"I","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1464","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16","scheme":"PositionToKnow","schemeID":"26"},{"nodeID":"1465","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:16"},{"nodeID":"1466","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:17"},{"nodeID":"1467","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:17"},{"nodeID":"1468","text":"RA","type":"RA","timestamp":"2012-04-12 17:22:17"}],"edges":[{"edgeID":"1344","fromID":"1455","toID":"1464","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1345","fromID":"1464","toID":"1454","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1346","fromID":"1456","toID":"1465","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1347","fromID":"1465","toID":"1454","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1348","fromID":"1457","toID":"1466","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1349","fromID":"1466","toID":"1454","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1350","fromID":"1458","toID":"1467","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1351","fromID":"1459","toID":"1467","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1352","fromID":"1460","toID":"1467","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1353","fromID":"1467","toID":"1456","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1354","fromID":"1461","toID":"1468","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1355","fromID":"1462","toID":"1468","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1356","fromID":"1463","toID":"1468","formEdgeID":null},{"edgeID":"1357","fromID":"1468","toID":"1457","formEdgeID":null}],"locutions":[{"nodeID":"1454","personID":"1244","timestamp":"2015-10-30 10:13:00","start":null,"end":null,"source":null},{"nodeID":"1455","personID":"1244","timestamp":"2015-10-30 10:13:00","start":null,"end":null,"source":null},{"nodeID":"1456","personID":"1244","timestamp":"2015-10-30 10:13:00","start":null,"end":null,"source":null},{"nodeID":"1457","personID":"1244","timestamp":"2015-10-30 10:13:00","start":null,"end":null,"source":null},{"nodeID":"1458","personID":"1244","timestamp":"2015-10-30 10:13:00","start":null,"end":null,"source":null},{"nodeID":"1459","personID":"1246","timestamp":"2015-10-30 10:13:00","start":null,"end":null,"source":null},{"nodeID":"1460","personID":"1246","timestamp":"2015-10-30 10:13:00","start":null,"end":null,"source":null},{"nodeID":"1461","personID":"556","timestamp":"2015-10-30 11:10:54","start":null,"end":null,"source":null},{"nodeID":"1462","personID":"556","timestamp":"2015-10-30 11:10:54","start":nul